95         |   sas -sysparm "C:\data\input|C:\data\output"
96         |       -sysin variable_info_cli20260320.sas
97         |
98         | Using a study-specific directory:
99         |   sas -sysparm "C:\studies\trial1\sas|C:\studies\trial1\output"
100        |       -sysin variable_info_cli20260320.sas
101        *------------------------------------------------------------------*/
